       Search Tips

     * Try a narrow scope search first by typing the exact phrase you are
       looking for. ie: "street lighting"
     * If you are not finding what you're looking for, try broadening your
       search. ie: light
     * You may also want to try our Site Map

                             Exact Phrase Search
      To search for an exact phrase: type in the words with or with out
                                   quotes
             ex: you are searching for the phrase "tax policies"
                tax policies________ OR "tax policies"______

                            Multiple Word Search
             To search multiple words: use AND to join the words
     ex: you want to find documents containing tax and policies but not
                            necessarily together
                            tax AND policies____

                            Excluded Word Search
             To exclude words: use AND NOT to exclude the words
       ex: you want to find documents containing tax BUT NOT policies
                            tax AND NOT policies

                             Either / Or Search
           To search in Either/Or Mode,: use OR to match the words
          ex: you want to find documents containing tax OR policies
                            tax OR policies_____

